### 🚢 Preparing for Deployment

To deploy on Render and Vercel, create these files:

#### For Render (Backend)
Create a `render.yaml` in the root:

```yaml
services:
  - type: web
    name: bridgehub-backend
    runtime: node
    repo: https://github.com/BrMwita/BridgeHub
    buildCommand: cd backend && npm install
    startCommand: cd backend && npm start
    envVars:
      - key: DATABASE_URL
        sync: false
      - key: JWT_SECRET
        sync: false
      - key: NODE_ENV
        value: production
